{"id": "cpos038", "name": "Audio_ruins08_702_12_26", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>Target hit rate 82%, revision rate 6%, power has returned to zero.</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke_Grenade", "Heat dissipates from gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... 6? Still no good?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "Dismantles Parts"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>Reassembling thermal dissolution unit code.</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "Dismantles Parts"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Overheats too easily... Can't get good material for dissipating heat here.\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "Dismantles Parts"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>Temperature test, 39 degrees, 40 degrees, 41 degrees...</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Not bad. That's more like it.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Ha... huff... shooting while moving is tough...\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "You're just too weak. But gotta say, with panting like that you did pretty good.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Come off it.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "When my dad used to teach me, I got stuck on this forever...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "When Mom left, Dad spent nearly all of his time with me. Felt like he was spending his whole life just to stop me from slipping into a negative emotional state... Back then, we loved watching the series \"Chrysanthemum\" together.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Ah, I remember that well. That show was on a long time ago. Our family liked it a lot too. It was really good.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Oh yeah? Then, I think he spent all of our money. That's when he got hooked on gambling. So, the gangs latched onto him. After that, he rarely spent time at home with me...\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "I still remember when the show came out with a second season. I couldn't wait to watch it. I waited everyday, kept waiting for him to come home and watch it with me. To this day, I still haven't finished it, haha... Really wanna know what happens to that girl who sells flowers.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I've got the whole series at home. I'll let you borrow it.\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Nah. My fans gave it to me for my birthday.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Haha... show-off.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Hehe... speaking of birthdays, back when Mom was still around they used to love surprising me to celebrate... Then it just stopped. I was so happy the first time they did that.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\nWhat's with all this recalling of old memories all of a sudden? You're like an old person.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Haha... donno. Seeing you practicing shooting and hearing the sound of guns makes me think of all that.\nAfter the first time Dad admitted to what was going on, he started teaching me to shoot. That's when I felt like I had found my family again...\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Lighting_smoke", "Lights Cigarette"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Here.\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Thanks.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke", "Inhales"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Ironic, right? What gives me a warm feeling of home is a cold, lifeless object.\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... That's only after you put it down, right? When you're shooting rapid-fire it's hot as all hell.\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Yeah...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "What violence is depends on how it's used, don't you think?\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "You remember me telling you how I stole my father's gun to save Shannon from that bully?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Yeah.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Later I heard Nate——a friend at the station, told me that dim-witted classmate who bullied my sister for years had gotten on the Exploration Team and became one of the elite members. When there were issues in the city, they came out and helped resolve them. Think I even know the captain.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "If my Dad hadn't shown up and I had fired that gun at ten years old... Just thinking about how many people's lives that would have affected makes me unconsciously hesitate whenever I shoot a firearm.\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... I get it.\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "So...\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Stands Up"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Since I'm learning all these techniques, I've got to think real hard about how to use 'em.\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Ha... Well put. But you've got to be a bit more accurate before you start spoutin' such pretty crap. Legs should be as wide as your shoulders, you forgot again.\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switches]</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>88 degrees, 89 degrees...</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke_Grenade", "Heat dissipates from gun"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "AH! Hot...!\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>Reassembly Complete</i>\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Stands Up"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Wide as my shoulders......</font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "Consecutive Gunshots"], "content": ""}, {"id": 61, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>命中率82%、補正率6%、パワーリセット。</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke_Grenade", "銃の放熱"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……6？まだダメか。\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "部品を外す"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>熱容器のコードを組み直します。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "部品を外す"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "熱を発しやすいな……\nここじゃいい放熱器を手に入れることはできない。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "部品を外す"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>温度テスト……39度、40度、41度……</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→ファイル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "へぇ、だいぶ良くなったんじゃん？\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "はっ……ハァ……移動しながらの射撃はやっぱり難しいな……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "それはあんたの体力がへぼ過ぎるだけ。\nでもそんだけゼェゼェしながら、この成績が出せたんなら悪くないよ。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "褒めるな。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "昔あたしが父さんに教わった時は、ここでつまづいたっけ……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "母さんがいなくなった時、父さんはずっとそばにいてくれた。\nまるで、自分の命をかけてでも、あたしを悲しみの中に閉じ込めさせはしないとでも言うようにさ……\nその時好きだったドラマがあってね。\n《Chrysanthemum》っていうんだけど。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "あぁ、懐かしいな。\nかなり昔のドラマだろ？\nうちも見てた。いいドラマだったよな。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "でしょ？\nでも、お金使いきっちゃったんだろうね。\n博打に打ち込むようになって……それでヤクザとも関わるようになったんだと思う。\nそれからは、家にいることも少なくなって、あたしのそばにもいてくれなくなった……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "あのドラマのシーズン2が放送され始めても、あたし見れなくて。\n毎日毎日……父さんと一緒に見るために、父さんの帰りを待ち続けた。\n未だに見終わってないとか笑えるでしょ……はは……\nあの花売りの女の子、どうなったのかな。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "うちに全部ある。\n貸すよ。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "いいよ。\n今年の誕生日にファンの子からもらったし。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "はは……自慢か？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "へへ……誕生日と言えばさ、母さんが生きてた頃はいつもサプライズしてもらってたなぁ……\nあれ以来、一切ないけど……だから、はじめてあんたたちに誕生日を祝ってもらった時はほんとに嬉しかったんだ。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\nさっきから昔話ばかり……急にどうしたんだ？\nババ臭いぞ。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "はは……さあね。\nあんたが銃の練習してるところを見ながら銃声を聞いてるとさ、思い出すんだよね。\n父さんがはじめてあたしに真実を打ち明けてくれてから銃の練習を始めて……あの時ようやく昔みたいに戻れた気がしたんだ……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Lighting_smoke", "タバコに火をつける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "ほら。\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ありがと。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke", "タバコを吸う"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "皮肉でしょ。\nあたしに家族のぬくもりを思い出させてくれるものは、こんな冷たい……拳銃なんだから。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……それはそこに置きっぱなしにしてるからだろ？\n何発か打てば熱くなる。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "まあね……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "武力ってものは、扱う人間によってまるで違うものになる。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Shannonを助けるために父親の銃を盗んだ話……覚えてるか？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うん。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Nate——管理局の友達に聞いたんだが、Shannonをいじめてた男は、数年間フラフラした後、今は探査隊として働いてるらしい。\nしかも優秀な探査隊員で、これまで町で何か問題が起きた時も何度も住人のために働いてるんだと。\n隊長は俺も知ってる男だ。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "もしあの時父さんが現れなかったら、まだガキだった俺は撃ってたかもしれない……\nその行為がどれだけの人の運命を左右するのかって考えたら、銃を撃つ時に無意識に迷いが生まれるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……わかるよ。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "だから……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "立ち上がる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "この手段を手に入れた今、使い道にはより慎重になるべきだ。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "はは……いいこと言うじゃん。\nでも、その程度の腕前じゃまだまだそんな偉そうなこと言えた立場じゃないけどね。\n足は肩幅。まーた忘れてたでしょ。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→ファイル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>88度、89度……</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke_Grenade", "銃が放熱する"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……っ！あつ……！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>完了しました。</i>\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "立ち上がる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">足は肩幅……</font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連続した銃撃"], "content": ""}, {"id": 61, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>命中率 82%，校正率 6%，功率歸零。</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke_Grenade", "槍枝散熱"], "content": ""}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……6？還是不行嗎？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Break_gun", "零件拆解"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>重組熱溶器編碼。</i>\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "零件拆解"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "太容易過熱了……這裡弄不到好的散熱材質。\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["ROBO_Servo", "零件拆解"], "content": ""}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>溫度測試，39 度、40 度、41 度……</i>\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換檔案]</i>\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "不錯，越來越有樣子了嘛。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "哈……呼……移動射擊還是好難……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "是你體力太差了，不過你喘成這樣還能有這種成績已經很不錯了。\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "不要誇我。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "以前我爸教我的時候我可是在這裡卡了好久……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "媽剛走的時候，爸幾乎花了所有時間來陪我，感覺像用他全部的生命在阻止我陷入悲傷的情緒裡一樣……那時候我們最喜歡一起看一部叫《Chrysanthemum》的電視劇。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "啊，好懷念，好久以前的影集了，我們家也很愛看，蠻好看的。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "對吧？後來他好像是把錢用光了，開始染上賭癮，所以才會被黑道的人勾搭上。從那之後他就很少在家裡陪我了……\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "我還記得後來那部電視劇出了第二季，我都一直捨不得看，每天一直等、一直等他回來陪我一起看，到現在我好像都還沒把那部劇追完，哈哈……好想知道那個賣花的女孩最後怎麼了。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我家有整套，可以借妳。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "不用啦，今年生日有粉絲送我了。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "哈哈……炫耀。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嘿嘿……說到生日，以前媽還在的時候，每次我慶生他們總喜歡給我驚喜……後來就再也沒有了，所以你們第一次幫我慶生那次，其實我真的很開心。\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n怎麼突然說起這些以前的事？像老人一樣。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哈哈……不知道，看著你練槍的背影，聽著這些槍聲總會讓我想到這些事情。\n爸第一次跟我坦白後，開始教我練槍，那時我才覺得重新找回以前一家人在一起那種感覺……\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Lighting_smoke", "點煙"], "content": ""}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "喏？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "謝謝。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke", "吸煙"], "content": ""}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "很諷刺對吧？用來讓我找回家的溫暖的，竟然是這種冷冰冰的東西。\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……那是因為放著吧？連續開個幾槍也是燙得跟什麼一樣的。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "武力這種東西，我覺得還是看人怎麼用吧？\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "妳還記得我上次跟妳說，小時候偷我爸的槍去救 Shannon 的事嗎？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "我後來聽 Nate——我在局裡的朋友說，那個霸凌我妹的同學，渾渾噩噩了幾年，現在好像在探勘隊服役，而且表現很優秀，不少次城裡出了問題他們小隊都有參與協助，他們隊長我也算認識。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "如果當時我爸沒有出現，十來歲的我就這麼不小心開了那一槍的話……光是想到這東西能影響多少人的命運，開槍時就會不自覺遲疑一下。\n"}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……我懂。\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "所以……\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "站立"], "content": ""}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "既然現在學會了這個技術，就要更謹慎思考怎麼利用。\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哈……說得真好，不過你還得再打準一點才有資格說這些漂亮話。腳，與肩同寬，你又忘了。\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換檔案]</i>\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>88 度、89 度……</i>\n"}, {"id": 54, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Smoke_Grenade", "槍枝散熱"], "content": ""}, {"id": 55, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "嘶！燙……！\n"}, {"id": 56, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["[Xenon A.I.]"], "content": "<i>重組完畢。</i>\n"}, {"id": 57, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 58, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "站立"], "content": ""}, {"id": 59, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">與肩同寬……</font>\n"}, {"id": 60, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Gun_Shot_Multi", "連續槍擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 61, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content":